dji.sdk.api.Battery

Class DJIBatteryState

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.Battery.DJIBatteryState

  • public class DJIBatteryState
extends java.lang.Object
    DJIBatteryState is designed for Inspire 1 and Phantom 3 and it would contain the information about the current state of the battery. The object of DJIBatteryState will record the information of dischargeOver, dischargeOverHeat, dischargeLowTemperature, short cut. Also, some values information about the battery will be recorded in the structure, too.
    Version:
    : V2.4.0
    Author:
    : DJI Software
